Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png'}
{3: 'I was never given a choice.'}
{3: 'Everything had been planned ever since I was born.'}
{3: 'Then came the virus outbreak. Most humans fled into the deep space of the universe.'}
{3: "It wasn't my choice either."}
{3: 'So, when this thing named "Punishing Virus" stood in front of me, and asked me the ancient question...'}
{3: 'How do you like half of the world?'}
{3: 'Yep. I had no choice. I had no other choice.'}
{3: 'The world fell into darkness, and I became the Lord of the Sky.'}
{1: 'DialogDisable'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory45.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Minion', 3: 'Overlord, our Construct squad was attacked by the Ascendants once again!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'So very careless... How embarrassing. And how many times do I have to tell you to not call me Overlord!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Minion', 3: 'Yes, Overlord!', 4: '1'}
{3: "The Overlord's powerful punch lands right on her minion's stomach, knocking him up so incredibly fast that he is launched out of Babylonia..."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Hassen', 3: "Umm... Overlord, please don't be mad. I say we send Gray Raven to handle this, what do you think?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Asimov', 3: "Right, he's right. I say we add Strike Hawk on top of that. They won't let you down.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "I still don't like that title, but whatever.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: "You must remember that Babylonia's goal is to rebuild Earth. Never let the Ascendants get in our way again.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Already waiting in the room, Gray Raven and Strike Hawk salute and leave.'}
{3: 'Hassen and Asimov quickly follow them out. The command room of Babylonia becomes quiet once again.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "Can't you just hold your breath, you stupid minion?!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Minion', 3: "That's way too hard... Urghhh!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'This time, the minion becomes a comet.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "What a pesky old man... And why don't you come out and introduce yourselves?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'Never thought you could find us. No wonder you were also favored by the Punishing Virus.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'Are you the leader of Ascendants?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: '???', 3: "Don't forget us, the Big Four of Ascendants.", 4: '1'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Self-Destruction Robot', 3: "And I'm the Third, the universal destruction, Self-Destruction Robot.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Riot Laser', 3: 'The Fourth, Riot, blinded by the laser, revved up like a deuce.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiSHanshuoNew.prefab'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: '...Ignoring how the Third and the Fourth look exactly the same, all you have is just a bunch of weirdos!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: 'Where are Gabriel, Roland, and Alpha?!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'Sorry, we had some internal workplace disputes recently... They even asked for a big compensation.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: "Um, I'll get the best lawyer for you...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: "Wait, we're not here for small talk!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: "I don't need your mercy. I'm going to defeat you, and sell Babylonia for money!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: "So you're really going to pay that compensation?!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Say no more. Big Four, attack!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'The Big Four', 3: 'Roger!'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "How pathetic. But I'm not going to hold back!", 4: '1'}
